headline: Northern Trust Asset Management Names New Head of Tactical Asset Allocation
summary: CHICAGO, November 13, 2024--Northern Trust Asset Management (NTAM), a leading global investment management firm with $1.3 trillion in assets under management as of September 30, 2024, announced Peter Wilke, CFA has joined as Head of Tactical Asset Allocation.
